Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:23.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4.533}告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.18,0:00:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉让你陪我到这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有女孩子在房间里等你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前已经告诉过她会晚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都这时候了应该没在等了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  JB
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个我…什么都没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你一定产生了很大的误会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听我解释
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是大人之间的玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  我不会和其他人说的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这样  其实口风很紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不信的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要立刻推到我  强吻一下看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说我接下来会被强暴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧  正好也有事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你烫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你的纽扣松了  帮你缝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要先洗个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我先洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要为我做到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了  对你一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能够接受这样的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,理由太过随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是雄二你不知道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有我这样子的女孩也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是小幸发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:57.42,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36.267\fad(0,500)}From  小幸\NTo       周防天音\N\N主题   我什么都没有说\N\N\N然后我什么都没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前也见过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫JB  是我的上司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上司？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这是她的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你不是讨厌别人过问你的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说你希望我去怀疑什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道雄二你想让我吃醋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没这打算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就吃下醋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来个吻的话  也许就原谅你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人  到底哪句真哪句假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说  她到底有多小看男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  闭上眼吧  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真强硬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…  可是第一次接吻啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真巧  其实我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉雄二的吻已经相当熟练了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  我下次会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这话是代表还有下次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是说说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  亲我原来只是玩玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说得这么难听
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是没有任何觉悟就做这种粗暴的行为的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你迷上我是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就认可了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我不能保证一生都能照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说  你承认我是你的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但你无法成为我的男朋友这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结论就是我可以成为你的女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但是有一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我突然消失  或者突然死去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在一年内  努力把我忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接受这些条件的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就可以成为你的女朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换  雄二你喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个希望你能现在就告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我对这方面的感情不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在对你的感情究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  能听到你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我现在就是雄二的女朋友了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突然一下子没力气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,膝盖不停地颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很开心  却没有什么实感
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  我是雄二的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来吧  来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要让我站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我可是无法反抗的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说  我在提示你现在可以把我上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  要做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会非常舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明全身都在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别太得意了  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确我没有和女生交往过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才想知道你为何如此想和我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了是一见钟情…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我  你这么做的原因是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,私立泷园学园1年A班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,篮球社成员  风见一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定认识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么认不认识  她是我姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,6年前的8月14日  女子篮球社
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在夏季合宿的回程路上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,包括她在内14人搭乘的小巴失去了踪迹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「泷园学园小巴坠崖事故」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那个事故中的唯一生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你的姐姐是同级生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么重要的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚转学过来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就马上发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有东西要给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是那天的日记
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,里面记载了所有的经过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,6年前的8月14日…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们结束了夏季合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在回去学校的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  是这条路没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小阿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,醒过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么能麻烦你从我身上移开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊  移动的时候小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:11:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我之后会去揍你的  告诉我你名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我开玩笑的  我叫风见一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫周防  周防天音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,周防同学吗  虽然知道名字和相貌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过和你说话是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬语就免了  我和你都是一年级生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  如果可以的话  能麻烦你赶紧从我身上下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第四次了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「对不起」这句话  说得越多就越不值钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再说的话  我可要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  从左边离开  出口在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是逃出生天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给  这是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来  我们该先去救谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二  你的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三  受伤的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让你选的话你会先救谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见同学想先救谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对提问人进行反问是很蠢的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别再干这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  那先救部长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我讨厌她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那问题的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我选四  先救我讨厌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,选四  你这是赖皮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,选项里面没有正确答案时你会怎么回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也包含在这个心理测试里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要先救自己讨厌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是有12个人要救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是自己讨厌的人留到最后再救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会感到厌烦的吧
